="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x74_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x75_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，则有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18307-formula435"><label>(1.5)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x76_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x77_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为正数。当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x78_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，上式仍然成立。</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18307-formula436"><label>(1.6)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x79_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.18307-formula437"><label>(1.7)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x80_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>其次在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x82_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中定义等价范数如下：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18307-formula438"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x83_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>由(1.5)~(1.7)，则有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18307-formula439"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x84_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x85_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，因此当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/5-2620288x86_hans